    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to pass this beauty along to its next home. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine, showroom condition. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! If you're looking for a ride that's been totally pampered and looks absolutely flawless, this is the one for you. Seriously, it's a dream! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
