    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a masterclass in atmospheric induction, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This collector-grade example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and features the M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains in impeccable form, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul to ensure mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry is tight, utilizing original-spec bushings and dampers that maintain the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory-original luster with no signs of oxidation or wear, while the undercarriage remains dry and pristine. A truly unmolested, turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Clean title. Full service records included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
