    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a genuine showroom-quality specimen, meticulously preserved to satisfy even the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a flawless, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented full service history and a spotless undercarriage that has never seen inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the day of its original delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
